deck: An American actor most well known for his role as Barry Allen in the television shows Arrow and The Flash.
description:
Comic Related Roles

Arrow

Gustin first appeared in the show as the character Barry Allen in the episode "The Scientist" in Season 2 of the TV Show Arrow. Barry is a CSI from Central City who arrives in Starling City stating that he believes that Super powered human beings exist and were responsible for the death of his mother when he was 11 years old.

Barry eventually saves Oliver Queen's life, and although Oliver is initially reluctant to trust Barry, he is eventually welcomed as apart of team Arrow. Barry seems to have a connection with Felicity Smoak, he tells her that if she decides that Oliver is not the right person for her than he will be there for her.

Barry returns to Central City in time for the activation of the particle accelerator. He is struck by a beam of lightning and left in a coma.

The Flash

Gustin will have the starring role as Barry in the The Flash TV Show.
name: Grant Gustin

deck: Josh Skidmore is the creator/writer and artist behind the new comic book series "The Awakened".  Josh has over 13 years experience with Adobe Photoshop, Illustrator and other various programs , bringing the world of "The Awakened" to life.
description: Identical twin to Jason Skidmore, Josh Skidmore is the creator/writer and artist behind the new comic book series "The Awakened". Josh has over 13 years experience with Adobe Photoshop, Illustrator and other various programs , bringing the world of "The Awakened" to life. Being a graphic designer, Josh displays outstanding skill and technique in his field.
name: Joshua Skidmore

deck: With over 10 years experience with photography, "Skidtography" owner Jason Skidmore specializes in a unique style of photography and projects becoming the first and primary photographer for the series "The Awakened".
description: Ever since Jason was a child he loved taking pictures of everything. As he grew up, he started to realize he had a eye for photography. He bought his first professional camera at the age of 22, and has since been doing photo shoots around the world. Over the years Jason has had the chance to meet and work with a lot of amazing people. Jason is a very open minded to all kinds of various shoots. Jason sees every shoot as a unique challenge, with unique possibilities.
name: Jason Skidmore

deck: Coming from a video game design back ground, Shane has a unique art style as well as style. Shane is now embarking on his first comic book series as is pre-photography storyboard artist.
description: Coming from a video game design back ground, Shane has a unique art style as well as style. Shane is now embarking on his first comic book series as is pre photography storyboard artist. Shane's job makes it easier for the photographer to capture the vision of the writers. When Shane isn't storyboarding, he is creating parts of the world of the Awakened by creating from scratch digital renders of locations, not in existence, thought up by the creators.
name: Shane Womboldt

description:
Terrio is most well known for writing the script for the 2012 Academy Award winning movie "Argo".

Terrio was also hired to rewrite the original script written by David S. Goyer for the Batman v Superman: Dawn of Justice film, directed by Zack Snyder. The film is set for release on March 25th, 2016. He is also set to write the screen-play for a Justice League based film, also directed by Zack Snyder.
name: Chris Terrio
